	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello all, lv 52 wiz on the quellious server here.<br><br>am thinking of organizeing a "Great Port Out".<br><br>what is this&nbsp;&nbsp;you ask....well...<br><br>One week of NOT porting anyone. (guildies and close freinds are the exception).<br><br>I think this will open peoples eyes to the importance of the wizzie and druid to the upper level game. <br><br>I know myself, i have not been in an exp group since about lv 38 or so. Anytime i am in a group, it is after much begging and doing 2 hours of /shout wizzie, tired of quading, seeks group.<br><br>so lets show those melle's we are useful. when they ask for ports say ..no..<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
