	   <tr><td colspan=2>Next time you feel the need to let a certain special someone or even a full group know the power you possess...<br><br>Well, let me tell you what I did.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Melee's had to break the mez.<br>Chanters mezzed the wrong things.<br>Healers healed the mobs.<br>Assist?  Whats assist?<br><br>So, out of my trusty aresenal of spells for just the right occasion, I made the words LOADING. PLEASE WAIT.  <br><br>When the group came to their senses, I was already back in the dreadlands, at the spot, forming a good group while they must have power leveled the 2 people in erudin to port them back.  Cazic Thule is nice too, it's a shame that there's an accept message on xlocs.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
