	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Even better...<br><br>Use the options--&gt;keyboard--&gt;go next until you get to user defined keys, then set user defined 6 to the right arrow key, and then put a sense heading hot button in that hot key slot.&nbsp;&nbsp;This way every time you click the right button walking around, it trys to hit sense heading hot key.  Keeps mine maxed 10 minutes into the next level.  After you max, then set the keyboard customization back to key 6, to get rid of the spam.<br><br>Just be careful NONE of your characters have an attack on that skill button, because you will hit it accidentally and attack something, probably a guard.  They keyboard mappings are for ALL characters.<br><br>Obon<br>26 Warrior on Vallon Zek<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
